&lt;p&gt;Charging your car should feel as natural as charging your phone. That&#39;s the future we&#39;re building: a network of EV chargers where life happens. We don&#39;t just install chargers. We &lt;strong&gt;accelerate sustainable mobility.&lt;/strong&gt; We &lt;strong&gt;obsess over partnerships.&lt;/strong&gt; We &lt;strong&gt;grow relentlessly&lt;/strong&gt;: our network, our partners, ourselves.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re here, you&#39;re probably not looking for &quot;just a job.&quot; Neither are we. 😎 We&#39;re driven by impact, and always looking for people who thrive on turning bold ideas into reality. If that sounds like you, you&#39;ll feel at home here. We&#39;re looking for people who see challenges as puzzles, not problems, thrive in fast-growing, high-energy environments, and want to shape the future of mobility, not just watch it unfold. At Powerdot, you&#39;ll get &lt;strong&gt;freedom&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;ownership&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;responsibility&lt;/strong&gt;. The space to experiment. The chance to scale your ideas. And a team that&#39;s always pushing the edge of what&#39;s possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🚀 About this Role&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;As our &lt;strong&gt;Data Analyst&lt;/strong&gt;, you&#39;ll be part of the Central Data team at Powerdot and will play a key role in the current phase of accelerated growth. Your mission is to transform raw data into clear, actionable insights that power smarter decisions across the business — ensuring every team has the visibility they need to move fast and move well. The ideal candidate has strong analytical and problem-solving skills, combined with the ability to communicate effectively with both technical and non-technical audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll Shape Our Story:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Your day-to-day will include&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gathering and transforming data from a variety of sources&lt;/strong&gt; — including internal databases, external APIs, and surveys, ensuring data is ready for analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analyzing data using statistical techniques&lt;/strong&gt; — identifying trends, patterns, and insights that drive smarter business decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Developing data visualizations&lt;/strong&gt; — creating clear, compelling dashboards and reports that communicate findings to stakeholders in a concise and actionable way.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partnering with stakeholders&lt;/strong&gt; — understanding their needs and developing data-driven solutions that address real business questions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Championing data quality&lt;/strong&gt; — maintaining and supporting a culture of strong data quality across teams and workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Staying ahead of analytics trends&lt;/strong&gt; — keeping up-to-date on the latest tools, techniques, and best practices in data analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentoring colleagues&lt;/strong&gt; — coaching co-workers on analytics best practices and helping elevate the team&#39;s overall data capability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This Is About You, Not Us 🫵🏼:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Up to 4 years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in data analytics or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
