&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt; Master&#39;s degree or equivalent preferred, ideally in Engineering or Business Management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 2–3 years of project management experience, preferably in the electrical or related fields.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;

